I never ask for a dime. Never ask for a dime and never will. But there's people that feel led to give to us and say, "Hey, I feel led to help you."And I say, "Okay."But I always take and pray over their stuff.

01:00:36.739 --> 01:00:56.519
And I spend a lot of time and my wife will write them a letter or whatever, but I lay my hands on it and I intercede and I ask for God to multiply it because I look at it as special that somebody would work really hard to try to help me.

01:00:56.520 --> 01:01:11.208
So I always take it, and my kids—Paisley and my son and everybody—we all lay hands on it, take communion over it, and I pray over the money and I say, "God, bless this."But I never know if my ground's good because how do you test your own ground?

01:01:11.209 --> 01:01:19.999
But I had a lady write a letter today and she said, "Ever since I started blessing your ministry, I've paid off all this stuff.

01:01:20.000 --> 01:01:26.345
I paid off my boat.""I paid off my RV that I had."She said, "I'm almost completely debt-free or whatever it was.

01:01:26.346 --> 01:01:41.565
I paid for all this stuff, and she said, 'I'm only a little bit until I'm debt-free with my house.'"And she said, "I believe it was because we gave to the ground."That blessed me a lot today.

01:01:41.566 --> 01:01:50.774
Like I said, I'm always curious about it. I know when I sow into certain ground, I know good ground.

01:01:50.775 --> 01:02:03.519
I test everybody's ground, and if I don't see good fruit in that ground, I don't give there. I don't always try to be polite about it; I'm just real.

01:02:03.520 --> 01:02:17.473
Because the Lord always said to me, "Brandon, don't ever give out of a feeling of necessity into certain ground.

01:02:17.474 --> 01:02:24.879
Always give whenever you're led by me. Money with a mission.

01:02:24.880 --> 01:02:31.999
Sow where I tell you to sow because not all ground will produce.

01:02:32.000 --> 01:02:36.795
Some ground is full of rocks. Some ground doesn't produce at all.

01:02:36.796 --> 01:02:50.345
But I want you to be strategic in your giving and the soil that I tell you to give into."So I pray about it a lot, and I sow into the ground.

01:02:50.346 --> 01:02:56.719
There's some ground that I give to and I never get fruit back—not very much.

01:02:56.720 --> 01:03:02.956
But then he says, "Give over here,"and it's fresh manure, and I'll get back a good harvest.

01:03:02.957 --> 01:03:12.319
He'll give me an idea. He'll tell me, "Go to this thrift store,"and usually it's in Edmond.

01:03:12.320 --> 01:03:22.919
"I want you to drive there."And there's a bunch of Brioni, a bunch of Chanel, and a bunch of this. A lady just dropped it off.

01:03:22.920 --> 01:03:41.011
"I want you to go in there, and you're going to make enough to pay all your bills for the month."I pray in the spirit and the Lord says, "Go over there."So I sow the seed and I believe for my need.

01:03:41.012 --> 01:03:48.789
The Lord says, "I want you to buy that. There's a lawnmower over here that is a good Honda lawnmower and you can flip it.

01:03:48.790 --> 01:04:01.879
Put it on Craigslist."So, I buy it for real cheap at the garage sale, put it on Craigslist, and flip it, making a couple hundred bucks. It's just following his voice.

01:04:01.880 --> 01:04:14.635
That's why I'm always pressing and asking him, "Show me."Then he started teaching me about crypto and about other things like cars. "This car over here, you can flip that car.

01:04:14.636 --> 01:04:28.719
It just needs a timing belt."There have been times he'll say, "The man with the white shirt is going to knock on the door, and that's the man who will buy the car today."I see the man with the white shirt.

01:04:28.720 --> 01:04:37.326
He's a Spanish man. He said, "This Hispanic man will knock on the door."I paid $800 for the car back then.

01:04:37.327 --> 01:04:42.296
My dad put the new timing belt on it and whatever else it needed.

01:04:42.297 --> 01:04:49.161
I sold it for $3,500. This was years ago, and that's how it's always happened.

01:04:49.162 --> 01:05:00.754
I listen. If you have an art of listening and praying, he'll teach you. But a lot of people are always looking for a handout.

01:05:00.755 --> 01:05:09.159
They're always looking for that mailbox mentality of a miracle because of what you've been taught at the charismatic shake and bake.

01:05:09.160 --> 01:05:19.388
I'm not into all that. I sow into strategic ground, and I believe that God will bless my hands. I'm not looking to people for a handout.

01:05:19.389 --> 01:05:29.743
I look to say, "God, show me what I can do."You go into a store, they have a 75% off sale, and you buy the rack of clothes.

01:05:29.744 --> 01:05:47.399
He goes, "Now flip that. Wait until spring of next year."Sure enough, what was on sale in 2023 becomes full price in 2024.

01:05:47.400 --> 01:05:52.599
And they don't know the difference. I'm not trying to deceive them, but they wanted the shirt.

01:05:52.600 --> 01:05:57.906
Do you know what I'm saying? You have to use wisdom in these last days.

01:05:57.907 --> 01:06:07.479
I'm telling you, God will take the foolish things of the world to confound the wise if you just listen to him.

01:06:07.480 --> 01:06:18.168
So there you go. You want to pray with me for a little bit? We can pray, and we'll pray over the nation.

01:06:18.169 --> 01:06:33.559
We'll pray over President Trump and the decisions of what he's really doing—not what he's telling you on TV.

01:06:33.560 --> 01:06:43.839
Don't be naive. Don't drink the Kool-Aid. You must come up higher in your spiritual walk with him.

01:06:43.840 --> 01:06:54.118
Stop being so naturally minded; you must think higher. He'll tell you the secret things if you just spend time with him.

01:06:54.119 --> 01:07:00.559
What you're hearing on the news right now is not what's really happening.

01:07:00.560 --> 01:07:12.769
If you're following the news, you're already too late. Braden always giggles because he knows what Daddy's thinking.

01:07:12.770 --> 01:07:18.719
I'm raising him so that whenever he gets married, his wife is going to have a good man.

01:07:18.720 --> 01:07:23.175
I kid you not. He knows how to pray in the spirit and how to do things.

01:07:23.176 --> 01:07:33.116
He is a very educated kid, especially biblically and prophetically. He is well-rounded; I have poured myself into him.

01:07:33.117 --> 01:07:41.514
I always say, "I will shelter you from any kind of harlot."We're not going to let any Delilah come up in here.

01:07:41.515 --> 01:07:53.519
You better listen to me. You're going to have Jesus all over you before you come around, my boy.

01:07:53.520 --> 01:08:04.159
It's only Jesus up in here. We don't have time for harlots. Father, we just thank you for the blood.

01:08:04.160 --> 01:08:09.187
We thank you, Father, for your goodness and your mercy tonight. We take the body, Father.

01:08:09.188 --> 01:08:22.239
We're so grateful for all that you've done for us—that you'll teach us the secret things that nobody else looks at because we have been with you.

01:08:22.240 --> 01:08:33.789
You'll teach us how to cure things through herbs. So many times, he'll tell me about herbs, roots, and berries.

01:08:33.790 --> 01:08:36.675
He said, "Brandon, I gave the herbs for the service of man."He talks about it in Genesis.

01:08:36.676 --> 01:08:59.519
He said, "So many people don't realize what's out there."I'll pray in the spirit, and he'll tell me exactly how to fix certain things.

01:08:59.520 --> 01:09:10.999
It's interesting, even when it comes to my little girl's new dog.

01:09:11.000 --> 01:09:15.419
Do you want to show them the dog after we pray? Yeah, go get the dog.

01:09:15.420 --> 01:09:23.192
I'll let them see it. Father, I take this body. We take it and we lift it up before you.

01:09:23.193 --> 01:09:35.879
We thank you, Father, that no weapon formed against us would prosper. We receive your healing, and it's already been done.

01:09:35.880 --> 01:09:42.919
You took it all for us, and we're so grateful that we are healed, whole, and well by your stripes.

01:09:42.920 --> 01:09:55.079
In Jesus'name, amen and amen. Father, we plead the blood of Jesus over us.

01:09:55.080 --> 01:10:00.742
We thank you, Lord, for the blood. You make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:10:00.743 --> 01:10:08.479
Come here, honey; this is my new baby. Father, we take communion.

01:10:08.480 --> 01:10:12.785
Father, we take the blood right now; we apply the blood even over Stella.

01:10:12.786 --> 01:10:25.599
We bless her. Is the internet out again? I don't know. Stay here and pray with me.

01:10:25.600 --> 01:10:34.334
Father, we thank you for the blood. We make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us. We thank you, Father, that it never loses its power.

01:10:34.335 --> 01:10:41.138
We plead the blood of Jesus over this house right now and everything that you have for us tonight.

01:10:41.139 --> 01:10:59.435
I don't think Starlink is hooked up outside, son. Did it just drop us? Is it gone?

